The '''Dhashaan Shield''' was a group of mercenaries formerly run by [[Dharus]]. They were hired by the [[Nhoras]] to fight the [[Clatear]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]] for 30,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] a day, as was their former leader who came out of retirement in order to lead them.

